'''威爾斯國旗'''（{{lang-cy|Y Ddraig Goch}}，意為[[紅龍_(威爾斯)|紅龍]]）是一面以白色和綠色為底色，中央有紅龍圖案的旗幟。紅龍圖案並無標準設計，存在多種外形，也因此這面旗幟並未出現在[[英國國旗|英國國旗]]中。

[[亨利七世_(英格蘭)|亨利七世]]可能在1485年[[博斯沃思原野戰役|博斯沃思原野戰役]]時曾使用這个旗幟。紅龍在都鐸王朝紋章中亦作為[[支撐物_(紋章學)|支撐物]]使用，以顯示其威爾斯血統。1959年，這面旗幟被正式承認為威爾斯国旗。包括威爾斯首府[[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]在內的部分威爾斯城市在其市旗中使用了紅龍設計。

== 歷史 ==
=== 可能起源於羅馬時期 ===
有歷史學家認為紅龍圖案起源於[[羅馬騎兵|羅馬騎兵]]的{{link-en|龍旗 (軍旗)|Draco (military standard)|龍旗}}。這些象徵在[[羅馬征服不列顛|羅馬征服不列顛]]時被帶入[[不列顛尼亞_(羅馬行省)|不列顛]]。而龍旗本身受到[[達契亞人|達契亞人]]或[[安息帝國|安息帝國]]象徵的啟發<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.data-wales.co.uk/flag.htm |work=Data Wales |title=The Welsh Flag and other Welsh symbols |first=John |last=Weston |access-date=2007-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071127034936/http://www.data-wales.co.uk/flag.htm |archive-date=2007-11-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。一個著名的影響威爾斯紅龍的龍旗象徵來自於撒馬利亞人，他們曾在2至4世紀駐紮在{{link-en|里布切斯特|Ribchester}}<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rees |first1=Huw |title=Enter the Dragon: the history of the Welsh flag revealed |url=https://www.thenational.wales/culture/19114269.revealing-secret-history-wales-flag/ |agency=The National |date=2021-02-24 |accessdate=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2021-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302153016/https://www.thenational.wales/culture/19114269.revealing-secret-history-wales-flag/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 在威爾斯神話和文學中的記載 ===
最早的有關威爾斯龍的記載是在成書於830年的《[[不列顛人的歷史|不列顛人的歷史]]》<ref name="Davies732">Davies (2008), pg 732.</ref>。紅龍的故事亦出現在散文集《[[馬比諾吉昂|馬比諾吉昂]]》<ref name="Davies732"/>。[[蒙茅斯的杰弗里|蒙茅斯的杰弗里]]在12世紀時的著作《[[不列顛諸王史|不列顛諸王史]]》亦有提及紅龍<ref name="Davies732"/>。

=== 歐文·格林杜爾 ===
1400年，[[歐文·格林杜爾|歐文·格林杜爾]]在其反抗英格蘭的戰爭期間曾使用「金龍旗」。當時的旗幟設計是在白底上描繪有金龍圖案<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8ipmBAAAQBAJ |title=Lost Battlefields of Wales |first=Martin |last=Hackett |date=2014-07-30 |publisher=Amberley Publishing Limited |isbn=9781445637037 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_p5DgK5GCGMC |title=A History of Wales |first=John |last=Davies |date=2007-01-25 |publisher=Penguin Adult |isbn=9780140284751 |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2020-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110052516/https://books.google.com/books?id=_p5DgK5GCGMC |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8XGoAwAAQBAJ |title=Owain Glyndŵr: The Story of the Last Prince of Wales |first=Terry |last=Breverton |date=2009-05-15 |publisher=Amberley Publishing Limited |isbn=9781445608761 |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105041640/https://books.google.com/books?id=8XGoAwAAQBAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

=== 亨利七世 ===
[[File:Royal_Standard_of_Henry_VII_of_England_(Dragon_and_flames).svg|thumb]]的旗幟，可能在1485年用於[[博斯沃思原野戰役|博斯沃思原野戰役]]]]
1485年，亨利七世在其入侵英格蘭時使用了紅龍標誌<ref name="dragon and war">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/history/sites/themes/society/flag_war.shtml |work=BBC |title=The dragon and war |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128093849/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/history/sites/themes/society/flag_war.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亨利七世有威爾斯血統。他在離開法國後帶領2,000人兵力登陸[[米爾福德港|米爾福德港]]，並以其威爾斯血統獲得在威爾斯的支持，順利穿過威爾斯。亨利七世在博斯沃思原野戰役中戰勝[[理查三世_(英格兰)|理查三世]]，並奪取英格蘭王位。在這場戰役之後，亨利將紅龍標誌帶入[[舊聖保羅座堂|聖保羅座堂]]，此後綠色和白色被加入旗幟中<ref>{{cite book |last=Perrin |first=W.G. |title=British Flags|url=https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.169115 |year=1922 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |location=Cambridge }}</ref>。

===現代旗幟===
1807年，紅龍圖案被加入[[威爾士皇家徽章|威爾士皇家徽章]]<ref name="Davies732"/>。1953年3月11日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fotw.net/flags/gb-wales.html |title=Origin of Y Ddraig Goch |work=Flags of the World |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2010-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611213215/http://fotw.net/flags/gb-wales.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，標語「{{lang|cy|Y Ddraig goch ddyry cychwyn}}」（意為「紅龍領路」）被加入紋章。這句標語由來於詩歌「{{lang|cy|Deio ab Ieuan Du}}」。而紋章則是威爾斯國旗的設計基礎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://flagspot.net/flags/gb-wa-hs.html |title=Wales: History of Welsh Flags |work=[[Flags_of_the_World_(website)|Flags of the World]] |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2017-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171125223310/https://flagspot.net/flags/gb-wa-hs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，被置於白綠兩色水平條紋上。然而這面旗幟成為被嘲諷的對象，原因之一是部分設計中的龍尾朝下<ref>{{cite web |last1=Raeside |first1=Rob |title=Origin of Y Ddraig Goch |url=https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/Flags/gb-wales.html |website=Flags of the World |access-date=2018-10-24 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125221416/https://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/gb-wales.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一原因是該標語有雙關之意，在原詩中暗示交配中的公牛陰莖 <ref name="Davies732"/><ref name="Eriksen&Thomas80">{{cite book |last1=Eriksen |first1=Thomas |last2=Jenkins |first2=Richard |title=Flag, nation and symbolism in Europe and America |url=https://archive.org/details/flagnationsymbol00jenk |date=2007 |publisher=Routledge |location=London |isbn=9780415444040 |page=[https://archive.org/details/flagnationsymbol00jenk/page/80 80] |edition=1. publ.}}</ref><ref name=Black109>{{cite journal |last1=Black |first1=Ronald |title=Studies in honour of James Carney (1914–89) |journal=Cambrian Medieval Celtic Studies |date=1992 |issue=23 |page=109 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yVopAQAAMAAJ&q=%22referring+to+the+bull+covering%22 |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2021-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210528101304/https://books.google.com/books?id=yVopAQAAMAAJ&q=%22referring+to+the+bull+covering%22 }}</ref>。1959年，政府改用現行旗幟設計<ref>Barraclough, EMC. ''Flags of the World'', 1965.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/written_answers/1959/feb/23/welsh-flag#S5CV0600P0-04661 |title=Welsh Flag (Hansard, 23 February 1959) |work=[[Hansard|Hansard]] |access-date=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506145352/http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/written_answers/1959/feb/23/welsh-flag#S5CV0600P0-04661 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。現在人們可在[[威爾士議會大廈|威爾士議會大廈]]等建築看到這面旗幟。

2017年，[[統一碼聯盟|統一碼聯盟]]在[[繪文字|繪文字]]中加入了威爾斯國旗<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2017/01/27/emoji-england-scotland-wales-flags-released-year/ |title=Emoji for England, Scotland and Wales flags to be released this year |last=Titcomb |first=James |date=2017 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |access-date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002020/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2017/01/27/emoji-england-scotland-wales-flags-released-year/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這一決定來自於[[表情圖示百科|表情圖示百科]]的{{link-en|傑瑞米·伯格|Jeremy Burge}}和[[BBC威爾士|BBC威爾士]]的歐文·威廉姆斯在2016年的提案<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-40032325 |title=Wales flag emoji arrives on Twitter |date=24 May 2017 |work=BBC News |access-date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200120145353/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-40032325 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-36985749 |title=Wales flag emoji decision awaited |last=Thomas |first=Huw |date=2016-08-05 |work=BBC News |access-date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104145959/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-36985749 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年[[英格蘭國旗|英格蘭國旗]]和[[蘇格蘭國旗|蘇格蘭國旗]]亦被加入主要智慧型手機平台<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-41839176 |title=Wales flag emoji arrives on iPhone |date=2017-11-01 |work=BBC News |access-date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807035546/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-wales-41839176 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此之前，《每日電訊報》曾報道用戶可以選擇英國國旗的繪文字，卻無法使用構成國的國旗<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/11/flags-england-wales-scotland-given-thumbs-emoji-chiefs/ |title=Flags of England, Wales and Scotland given thumbs up by emoji chiefs |date=2016-12-11 |work=The Daily Telegraph |access-date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125195603/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/11/flags-england-wales-scotland-given-thumbs-emoji-chiefs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

