==聖大衛旗==
{{main|聖大衛旗}}
[[File:Flag_of_Saint_David.svg|thumb]]
[[聖大衛旗|聖大衛旗]]是一面黑底上有黃色十字的旗幟，被使用在[[聖公會聖戴維茲教區|聖公會聖戴維茲教區]]的紋章上，並飄揚在[[聖大衛日|聖大衛日]]時。部分組織傾向使用聖大衛旗作為威爾斯的標誌，理由是他們對現在的威爾斯國旗並不滿意<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/christian-group-wants-evil-welsh-2263878 |title=Christian group wants 'evil' Welsh flag changed |date=2007-03-03 |website=Wales Online |access-date=2017-12-12 |archive-date=2016-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131045825/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/christian-group-wants-evil-welsh-2263878 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==流行文化==
威爾斯國旗在藝術、體育和商業領域均被作為威爾斯的象徵。在威爾斯舉辦的{{link-en|1999年世界盃橄欖球賽|1999 Rugby World Cup}}上，開幕式多次使用了龍的圖案。威爾斯國旗圖案還被用作威爾斯歌手[[雪莉·貝西|雪莉·貝西]]所穿裙子的圖案<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/wales/461052.stm |title=World Cup kicks off in style |work=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] |date=1999-10-01 |accessdate=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2022-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402034930/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/wales/461052.stm }}</ref>。

亦有眾多音樂人使用威爾斯國旗，包括[[狂街傳教士|狂街傳教士]]的{{link-en|尼基·威爾|Nicky Wire}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/music/sites/manic-street-preachers/pages/nicky.shtml |title=Manic Street Preachers – Nicky Wire |publisher=BBC Wales Music |accessdate=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519102124/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/music/sites/manic-street-preachers/pages/nicky.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{link-en|凱莉·馬修斯|Cerys Matthews}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/pop-music-the-changing-face-of-brit-guitar-rock-1152664.html |title=Pop music: The changing face of Brit guitar rock |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=1998-03-27 |accessdate=2021-05-21 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220214117/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/pop-music-the-changing-face-of-brit-guitar-rock-1152664.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及古典音樂歌手[[凱瑟琳·詹金斯|凱瑟琳·詹金斯]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/showbiz/article-23543895-katherine-jenkins-threatens-to-spill-out-of-dress-on-stage-as-boyfriend-gethin-jones-looks-on.do |title=Katherine Jenkins threatens to spill out of dress on stage as boyfriend Gethin Jones looks on |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405072446/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/showbiz/article-23543895-katherine-jenkins-threatens-to-spill-out-of-dress-on-stage-as-boyfriend-gethin-jones-looks-on.do |archive-date=2010-04-05 |work=Evening Standard |date=2008-08-25 |accessdate=2021-05-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2018年，威爾斯國旗在電影[[黑豹_(電影)|黑豹]]中的[[聯合國總部大樓|聯合國總部大樓]]場景出現。人們因此猜測威爾斯在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]是獨立國家。這也引發了議論，威爾斯政府和威爾斯民族主義政黨[[威爾士黨|威爾士黨]]均對此發表評論<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brennan |first1=Shane |title=Marvel movie franchise recognises Welsh independence |url=https://www.dailypost.co.uk/news/north-wales-news/wales-wins-independence-united-nations-14298958 |access-date=2021-03-12 |agency=North Wales Live |date=2018-02-16 |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515180515/https://www.dailypost.co.uk/news/north-wales-news/wales-wins-independence-united-nations-14298958 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Black Panther's universe features an 'independent Wales' |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/newsbeat-43085864 |access-date=2021-03-12 |agency=BBC |date=2018-02-16 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162956/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/newsbeat-43085864 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Williams |first1=Kathryn |title=Welsh flag flies as independent state in Marvel superhero film Black Panther |url=https://www.walesonline.co.uk/whats-on/film-news/welsh-flag-flies-independent-state-14296040 |access-date=2021-03-12 |agency=Wales Online |date=2018-02-16 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024121257/https://www.walesonline.co.uk/whats-on/film-news/welsh-flag-flies-independent-state-14296040 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

